name: #3 ANGUISH
description: The one who devoured his own kind was Anguish, his hunger had gone insane so the guild sealed him inside the Fortress of the Forbidden where unimaginable horrors had occurred. When Hunters entered the Fortress, breaking the seal the beast awoke after centuries of slumber, furious and famished. The empty towers were soon painted in blood and filled with screams of the feasted.
